Friends from the gang, help!

515
00:34:37,416 --> 00:34:41,076
That's what 70 centimeters
of reinforced concrete does.

516
00:34:41,791 --> 00:34:45,421
It's like shouting in a submarine
at the bottom of the sea.

517
00:34:54,083 --> 00:34:55,293
Third card...

518
00:34:56,500 --> 00:34:57,580
to draw blood.

519
00:35:01,083 --> 00:35:02,753
I'm going out for a moment.

520
00:35:14,625 --> 00:35:17,625
