528
00:35:50,666 --> 00:35:52,626
palpitations, attacks, dude.

529
00:35:53,750 --> 00:35:57,000
I've only been able to sleep
knowing she was by my side.

530
00:35:57,958 --> 00:35:59,788
Do you know what I mean?

531
00:36:01,958 --> 00:36:04,578
You sleep with her
and tell me to my face.

532
00:36:05,583 --> 00:36:10,463
