534
00:36:19,708 --> 00:36:22,538
- I'm your friend.
- Doesn't seem like it.

535
00:36:27,166 --> 00:36:28,626
Jesus fucking Christ!

536
00:36:29,791 --> 00:36:32,461
Your helmet! Your vest!

537
00:36:32,541 --> 00:36:34,041
Put pressure on it!

538
00:36:34,916 --> 00:36:36,206
Denver, hold on!

539
00:36:44,583 --> 00:36:47,083
- Bogotá, Nairobi, location?
- Elevator.

540
00:36:47,166 --> 00:36:49,286
We're OK. And Denver and Rio?

541
00:36:49,666 --> 00:36:50,876
Denver, Rio.

542
00:36:52,166 --> 00:36:53,916
- Denver, Rio.
- I'll go.

543
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:56,170
No, you stay with the hostages.

544
00:36:56,250 --> 00:36:57,920
Come on, Helsinki.

545
00:37:10,125 --> 00:37:12,415
Careful, the bastard's here somewhere.

546
00:37:25,125 --> 00:37:27,785
It was in the elevator
on the first floor.

547
00:37:27,875 --> 00:37:28,955
Received.

548
00:37:30,083 --> 00:37:32,713
He may be nearby. We'll stay here.

549
00:37:35,416 --> 00:37:36,576
Come on, big man.

550
00:37:54,125 --> 00:37:55,535
Stay calm. We're here!

551
00:37:58,625 --> 00:38:00,875
- Get up.
- Denver.

552
00:38:01,666 --> 00:38:03,076
Are you OK?

553
00:38:03,166 --> 00:38:04,576
Are you OK?

554
00:38:10,875 --> 00:38:11,825
Are you OK?

555
00:38:15,500 --> 00:38:17,420
Get down!

556
00:38:28,833 --> 00:38:30,503
Motherfucker!

557
00:38:34,458 --> 00:38:35,668
We're taking fire!

558
00:38:35,750 --> 00:38:38,380
First floor, elevator.
Reinforcements, now!

559
00:38:39,541 --> 00:38:40,501
Go.

560
00:38:44,541 --> 00:38:45,831
Go.

561
00:40:40,958 --> 00:40:43,668
Third time's the charm, mutt.
